[A number of contributors have called this situation to my attention over
the past two days. I have delayed posting it since it is not clear the
extent to which this represents the expected incidence of invasive
streptococcal infections as opposed to a cluster of epidemiologically
related cases. The involvement of CDC personnel suggests that something
unusual may be occurring. - Mod.ES]
